events.text: They are dealt with, but now... I gotta take care of the escaped fruits...
There has to be over 30 at least. This should go well...
They even broke trough the 3 layers of watchers.
Luckily, there was a recycling bin blocking the way, and I picked up trash along the way.
But I must do this... for my village, and for the future of our climate.
